<h3 id="_3-3-累积分布函数-cdf" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-3-累积分布函数-cdf"><span>3.3 累积分布函数（CDF）</span></a></h3>
<p>由定义：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>δ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>δ</mi></msubsup><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(\delta) = \int_{-1}^{\delta} p(t)\,dt
