归一化常数为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo fence="false" stretchy="true" minsize="1.8em" maxsize="1.8em">[</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>δ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><msub><mi>η</mi><mi>m</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>δ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><msub><mi>η</mi><mi>m</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo fence="false" stretchy="true" minsize="1.8em" maxsize="1.8em">]</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Z = 1 - \frac{1}{2}\Big[(1 - \delta_1)^{\eta_m + 1} + (1 - \delta_2)^{\eta_m + 1}\Big].
