<p>随机生成 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>∼</mo><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u \sim U(0,1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∼</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，则扰动 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">Δ</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">q</span></span></span></span> 的计算为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>q</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">{</mo><mtable rowspacing="0.36em" columnalign="left left" columnspacing="1em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="false"><mrow><msup><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mtext> </mtext><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>δ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><msub><mi>η</mi><mi>m</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext> </mtext><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mtext>mut_pow</mtext></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="false"><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="false"><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mtext> </mtext><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>δ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><msub><mi>η</mi><mi>m</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext> </mtext><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mtext>mut_pow</mtext></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="false"><mrow><mi>u</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0.5.</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta q =
\begin{cases}
\left[\,2u + (1 - 2u)(1 - \delta_1)^{\eta_m + 1}\,\right]^{\text{mut\_pow}} - 1, &amp; u \le 0.5, \\[8pt]
